licence_overview:
Centres of learning including colleges, employers and private training providers who provide vocational training in Scotland need approval from the [Scottish Qualifications Agency (SQA).](http://www.sqa.org.uk/sqa/CCC_FirstPage.jsp "Scottish Qualifications Agency"){:rel="external"}

This includes the provision of training leading to external qualifications including, but not limited to, [Scottish Vocational Qualifications.](http://www.sqa.org.uk/sqa/2.html "Scottish Vocational Qualifications"){:rel="external"}

All new external qualifications offered in Scotland are required to be accredited by the SQA.

*[SQA]:  Scottish Qualifications Agency
